cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper proposes a novel attention model for semantic segmentation, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the proposed attention model involves learning to weight features, which could be related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper evaluates its approach on image datasets, which could also suggest cs.MM (Multimedia).
